headline: A Look At Trane Technologies (TT) Valuation After Strong Q4 Beat And Upbeat 2026 Guidance
summary: Trane Technologies (TT) just reported fourth quarter 2025 results that came in ahead of analyst expectations on both revenue and earnings, paired with strong bookings, a record backlog, and upbeat 2026 guidance. See our latest analysis for Trane Technologies. At a share price of $420.58, Trane has had a 7 day share price return of 8.9% and a 30 day share price return of 8.1%.
